data.description: Now offering a 4.375% assumable VA mortgage for qualified borrowers! Back on market at no fault of the sellers!! Home was inspected and passed appraisal! Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful Ravenwood subdivision of Boiling Springs, SC! This meticulously maintained one-level home is the epitome of comfort and style, offering an array of desirable features that are sure to impress even the most discerning home buyers. Step inside and be greeted by the spacious great room, boasting 9-foot ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere. The seamless flow between the great room and the open kitchen floor plan is a true entertainer's delight, allowing you to host gatherings and create memories with ease. The kitchen itself is a chef's paradise, with ample counter space, modern appliances, and a convenient layout that makes cooking a breeze. Throughout the home, you'll discover the exquisite beauty of bamboo flooring, adding a touch of elegance and sustainability to every room. The owners have gone above and beyond with their remodel, ensuring that every detail is perfect. The full bathroom remodels showcase the latest in design and functionality, while the fresh coat of paint gives the home a renewed vibrancy. One of the highlights of this property is the addition of an extra concrete pad, offering versatility and convenience for your outdoor needs. Whether you envision it as a spot for additional parking or as a foundation for your outdoor projects, this feature truly sets this home apart. The master bedroom is a sanctuary in itself, providing ample space for a king-sized bed and a relaxing ambiance. The remodeled master bathroom features a luxurious walk-in shower and a spacious closet, completing this private retreat. The additional bedrooms offer generous dimensions, ensuring that everyone in the household enjoys their own space and privacy. Comfort and relaxation are at the forefront of this home's design, allowing you to unwind and recharge at the end of each day. As you step outside, you'll be captivated by the covered back porch patio, the perfect spot for afternoon relaxation or weekend cookouts with friends and family. The fully fenced backyard ensures privacy and security, while the shade trees create a tranquil setting that beckons you to enjoy the outdoors. With the addition of raised bed gardening, cultivating your own vibrant oasis is within reach. The Ravenwood community is known for its peacefulness, providing a serene backdrop for daily living. Residents can take advantage of the refreshing in-ground pool, a wonderful amenity for those hot summer days when you need to cool off and unwind. Don't miss the opportunity to make this gem of a home yours. Schedule your visit today and experience the comfort, style, and tranquility that await you in this exceptional property.
